{"tid":1726130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認識鼠疫","createTime":"2019-11-16T04:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T03:53:35.000Z","uid":273834,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"486ba0d6c4b0d88b63513d017b138c222acc2b8f","tid":1726130,"uid":273834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:21:24.000Z","msg":"Plague 鼠疫/黑死病<br />\n<br />\n成因<br />\n <br />\n由細菌  Yersinia pesti 引起. 鼠類為帶菌者，人類可由被感染鼠身上的蝨咬而患上，其他有可能途徑為照顧受感染兔類、松鼠、土撥鼠或家貓，身上有傷口亦可被感染。<br />\n <br />\n發病情況有三種包括：淋巴核、肺部感染或細菌入血<br />\n<br />\n其中肺部感染病人可經飛沫傳播給其他人，這就是疫症蔓延的開始<br />\n<br />\n由感染至病發一般為二至八日。肺感染可以短至一日<br />\n<br />\n病癥病狀<br />\n<br />\n發燒、打冷震、疲倦、頭痛、喉嚨痛、肌肉痛、抽筋癲癇、腋下大腿間頸後有淋巴位發脹；<br />\n<br />\n嚴重咳嗽、呼吸困難及胸痛、痰中帶血、肚痛肚瀉、毆吐、容易出血、手指腳趾鼻發黑、血壓驟降。<br />\n<br />\n化驗項目<br />\n從血液、痰及針刺抽取淋巴核種菌<br />\n肺部X光片<br />\n <br />\n治療<br />\n發病後二十四小時內接受治療，否則有性命<br />\n <br />\n抗生素streptomycin, gentamicin, doxycycline, chloramphenicol, moxifloxacin or ciprofloxacin<br />\n氧氣、靜脈血管輸液、用儀器維持呼吸<br />\n隔離病者，與患者有緊密接觸的人考慮預防性抗生素<br />\n <br />\n沒有預防疫苗<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n如沒有適當治療<br />\n<br />\n一般淋巴核感染者一半會死亡<br />\n<br />\n而肺部或血液感染近乎全部死亡<br />\n<br />\n適當治療亦只能減少死亡率一半!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/000596.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedlineplus.gov%2Fency%2Farticle%2F000596.htm&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=41fff4f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/000596.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/plague/diagnosis-treatment/drc-20351297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fplague%2Fdiagnosis-treatment%2Fdrc-20351297&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=9bb39fbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/plague/diagnosis-treatment/drc-20351297</a>"},{"pid":"1ce2eca70d412d59058e01d9244d21f21323dc6f","tid":1726130,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:56:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd82dd1bd2e55a4aebb6faa5d36f4e4c24f6fe53","tid":1726130,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"普通口罩阻唔阻到飛沫傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9131fd9b3a55891af0602aacacad76d6e4ec2611","tid":1726130,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd82dd1bd2e55a4aebb6faa5d36f4e4c24f6fe53","tid":1726130,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"普通口罩阻唔阻到飛沫傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:53:35.000Z","msg":"最好就N95啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}